==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: ĭd'ē-əm
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ˈɪdɪəm/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /"IdI@m/

=== Noun ===
# A [[phrase]] that cannot be fully understood from the separate meanings of the individual words which form it, but instead must be learned as a whole unit of meaning.
#: ''You can't translate that literally.  It's an idiom.''
# A manner of speaking, a way of expressing one's self

